Update AccountingTRSReportLayout and Input classes
The AccountingTRSReportLayout class has been simplified by removing the rendering of the 'created_at' field's date calculation. The Input class now includes methods for 'relativeTime', 'timestamp', and 'parsedTime' which handle time-related inputs in a more organized and efficient manner. This modification enhances code readability and time calculation efficiency.

Update AccountingTRSReportLayout and Input classes
The AccountingTRSReportLayout class has been simplified by removing the rendering of the 'created_at' field's date calculation. The Input class now includes methods for 'relativeTime', 'timestamp', and 'parsedTime' which handle time-related inputs in a more organized and efficient manner. This modification enhances code readability and time calculation efficiency.

Add relative-time tag to input field
Implemented a new 'relative-time' tag to the input field view to handle time inputs. This tag correctly renders elapsed time from the given timestamp. Additionally, a conditional was added to maintain the previous 'datalist' behavior when 'relativeTime' was not used.

Add default cursor and update collaborative session in Quill controller
Added a default cursor initialization in the Quill controller. Also, the users joining/leaving actions inside the initCollaboratives() method have been modifed without clearing all cursors each time a user joins or leaves, allowing each user to have a unique, persistent cursor during their session.

Correct capitalization in namespaces
Fixed capitalization issue in namespaces across VisitsStatistics model and VisitTracker middleware. Made sure that all namespaces start with a capital 'A' to follow the conventions and avoid any potential errors or issues.
